title: #105 - Logic
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we are joined by rapper/author/writer/cool dude Bobby Hall aka Logic!!! Together we discuss the pressures of fame, social media, tough childhoods, the nature of a piece of art, meeting Eminem and Jerry Seinfeld, and people creeping under the bathroom stall! Logic's book Supermarket will be on sale March 24th and is available for pre-order now!
